                <img src="/medias/youpai/又拍云_logo6.png" width="65px" style="vertical-align: middle">
            </a>提供CDN加速/云存储服务
            <br>
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m4 l4 social-link <%- socialClass %>"><%- partial('_partial/social-link') %></div>
